    # Look through https://st.yandex-team.ru/DEVTOOLSSUPPORT-39642 for more information.
    FORK_SUBTESTS()

    # TAG and REQUIREMENTS are copied from: https://docs.yandex-team.ru/devtools/test/environment#docker-compose
